snippet.title: CD 2: Trap Master - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Next August 2023
snippet.description: Get a deep dive into CDII: Trap Master in this latest trailer, including gameplay, a peek at your adventure, strategies, enemies, and more from this upcoming 3D tower defense and roguelike deckbuilding game. In CDII: Trap Master, craft a deck, lay out traps, ward off enemies, and navigate through the map until you confront the boss. Make use of a variety of funny and creative traps to shoot, stab, and scorch enemies. CDII: Trap Master is coming to PC, and a demo is available now on Steam.
